toast.success(response.data); //setCartpg(response.data) }, (error) =>{ console.log(error); toast.error("error"); } ); navigate("/Cartlist") }; useEffect(() => { fetchProperty(); fetchReview(); }, []); console.log(response.data.facilities); console.log(facilities.type); } catch (error) { console.error('Error fetching property details:', error); } }; const fetchReview = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get(`http://localhost:8080/review/${item_value}`);
